Hallo Thomas,

Anbei die Unterlagen zu den Container der letztlich verschick wurde. Bitte =
schick uns den Trackinglink wenn verf=C3=BCgbar.

Bereits vielen Dank.

Mit sportlichen Gr=C3=BC=C3=9Fen,
Theo Weyers


T: +31 85 5800 800 |=20
W: www.fitness-seller.nl |=20
A: Dr. Nolenslaan 113, 6136 GM, Sittard, The Netherlands
The contents of this message are confidential. If you have received it in e=
rror, please let us know and then delete it. It is prohibited to copy, forw=
ard, or otherwise disclose the contents of this message to anyone. The inte=
grity and security of this email cannot be guaranteed. Therefore, the sende=
r cannot be held liable for any damages caused by this message.

